:: Start {"position":"800,500","size":"100,100"}
In the world of Panini, lies a vast selection of mountain ranges, each characterized in their own unique shapes and colors.

Among the mountains, stood the tallest one of all. Upon closer inspection, reveals a small silhouette journeying through a towering mountain path, its tiny feet waddling in wide strides on cold stone dust.

Cold wind brushes against its soft feathers as the path grows steeper and steeper.

But at last, the little creature finally reaches the summit.

